    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是付费接口的意思。EMR同步完成后要回到诊断引擎做路由决策，这个决策节点分出三条路径：实验室分析、患者记录、以及回到引擎本身。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主链路：A诊断引擎通过Get money连线到B的EMR同步，然后B指向C决策节点。三条分支分别标注One、Two、Three，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "One",
        "Two",
        "Three"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "One指向HealthTech_LabAnalyzer实验室分析，Two指向HealthTech_PatientRecords患者记录，Three要闭环回到HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "One",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "Two",
